[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Cycle signal types]]


Set which type of signal should be cycled through when ctrl-clicking on a ready-built signal. Choose between cycling through all [[en/Manual/Signals]] types, just the [[en/Manual/Signals]] types or only the [[en/Manual/Signals]] types.

0 = Block signals only
1 = Path signals only
2 = All

See also: [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Advanced Settings/Construction#cycle-through-signal-types]]